<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='600082' id='t-600082'>or give me one as a gift,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='602260' id='t-602260'>it will be the same good.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='603620' id='t-603620'>It will work the same either way.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='606106' id='t-606106'>But the same may not be true</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='608882' id='t-608882'>if we're talking about nonmaterial goods</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='611214' id='t-611214'>and social practices such as teaching and learning</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='615164' id='t-615164'>or engaging together in civic life.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='618896' id='t-618896'>In those domains, bringing market mechanisms</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='622317' id='t-622317'>and cash incentives may undermine</span>
