<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='662935' id='t-662935'>values and attitudes worth caring about.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='665938' id='t-665938'>But to have this debate,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='669200' id='t-669200'>we have to do something we're not very good at,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='672698' id='t-672698'>and that is to reason together in public</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='676180' id='t-676180'>about the value and the meaning</span>
