<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='706244' id='t-706244'>our public discourse during this time</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='709726' id='t-709726'>has become hollowed out,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='711961' id='t-711961'>empty of larger moral meaning.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='715667' id='t-715667'>For fear of disagreement, we shrink from these questions.</span>
