</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:04
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='773211' id='t-773211'>This isn't good for democracy,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='775760' id='t-775760'>nor is it a satisfying way to live,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='778683' id='t-778683'>even for those of us who can afford</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='781963' id='t-781963'>to buy our way to the head of the line.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='784718' id='t-784718'>Here's why.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='786491' id='t-786491'>Democracy does not require perfect equality,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='791420' id='t-791420'>but what it does require</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='793183' id='t-793183'>is that citizens share in a common life.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='796811' id='t-796811'>What matters is that people</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='799440' id='t-799440'>of different social backgrounds</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='801209' id='t-801209'>and different walks of life</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='802933' id='t-802933'>encounter one another,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='805217' id='t-805217'>bump up against one another</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='807240' id='t-807240'>in the ordinary course of life,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='810730' id='t-810730'>because this is what teaches us</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='813454' id='t-813454'>to negotiate and to abide our differences.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='817126' id='t-817126'>And this is how we come to care for the common good.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:52
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='821340' id='t-821340'>And so, in the end, the question of markets</span>
